Package org.gbif.api.vocabulary

Enum Class Language

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Language>
org.gbif.api.vocabulary.Language
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Language>, Constable
public enum Language extends Enum<Language>
Enumeration for all ISO 639-1 language codes using 2 lower case letters. The enumeration maps to 3 letter codes and Locales.
See Also:
  • Wikipedia on ISO-639
  • Locale javadoc
